<Algorithm code="         1. If _validElementTypes_ is not present, set _validElementTypes_ to ~all~.         1. If _obj_ is not an Object, throw a *TypeError* exception.         1. Let _len_ be ? LengthOfArrayLike(_obj_).         1. Let _list_ be a new empty List.         1. Let _index_ be 0.         1. Repeat, while _index_ &lt; _len_,           1. Let _indexName_ be ! ToString(𝔽(_index_)).           1. Let _next_ be ? Get(_obj_, _indexName_).           1. If _validElementTypes_ is ~property-key~ and _next_ is not a property key, throw a *TypeError* exception.           1. Append _next_ to _list_.           1. Set _index_ to _index_ + 1.         1. Return _list_.       ">
